a.n: I HAVE SEEN THE EARTH CHANGE - NETHERLANDS: A COUNTRY BENEATH THE SEA

p.k: Global warming causes the icecap to melt which induces a rise in sea level. A nightmare for the Dutch since 60% of their territory lies below that very sea level. This concerns Oebele Wiedjik who lives in a polder. Oebele Wiedjik is a farmer.
